{
  "text": "We proceed to review succintly our construction given in full detail in [CITATION_1] . Given a CP semigroup (\u03c6 t ) t\u22650 of B(H 0 ) with minimal dilation \u03b1, we obtain a product system E \u03c6 that is canonically isomorphic to E \u03b1 .",
